Our Customer Portal is where you can manage your hosting services, domains, billing, and support tickets. Follow the steps below to log in.

Step 1: Go to the Login Page

Open your browser and visit:
https://petalhost.com/members/login

Step 2: Enter Your Login Details

In the Email Address field, enter your registered email address.

In the Password field, enter your account password.


Step 3: Click Login

Once your details are entered, click the Login button to access your account.
